Results.ReviewText: I just love Nescafe decaff coffee. so full of flavour and goes down a treat. Having sleep apnea my nurse suggestd not having caffeine coffee anymore and to switch to decaff. Since i tried Nescafe decaff i havent gone back.
Results.Title: Love Nescafe

Results.ReviewText: When I was told that I had to stop drinking coffee for medical reasons I was very upset but I have now replaced my original coffee with Nescafe Decaf and I am delighted to say it really has a good taste.  Thank you Nescafe
Results.Title: Surprisingly Good

Results.ReviewText: I have always drank nescafe original (for over 30 years now), but recently have been advised to cut out caffeine as I have high blood pressure... so I changed to nescafe decaf.... same great taste and alot less caffeine.
Results.Title: great taste

Results.ReviewText: I used to buy Nescafé Original but after trying the decaf, I have stopped as the taste is just as good and it is better for me. My daughter has also stopped and when given other brands, the difference is very noticeable.
Results.Title: Good taste

Results.ReviewText: I find myself being quite sensitive to caffeine but was unsure if this version would be as good as the original. It absolutely is! All the flavour and top quality I expect from Nescafe without the extra caffeine content.
Results.Title: Just as good as the original

Results.ReviewText: Advised to go Decaff, but need not have worried as Nescafe Decaff is as good as Nescafe Original but decaffeinated, same great taste and flavour. My doctor is happy and I'm very happy, a winning trio with Nescafe Decaff.
Results.Title: Decaffantastic

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe have used their expertise and created a decaff coffee I can relax with in the evening. I enjoy the smooth flavour and the wonderful aroma of quality coffee. I sometimes add a few cheeky marshmellows on top. Yum!
Results.Title: Best tasting decaff

Results.ReviewText:
I like my coffee natural, I like the smooth rich taste
I never leave it in my cup, I couldn't bear the waste
My coffee keeps me fresh, through the long, long working day
I love my Nes Decaff - pure value all the way
Results.Title: Can't do without it!

Results.ReviewText: I love the taste of Nescafé but find that the caffeine gives me too much of a 'buzz' if I drink it frequently. With Nescafé Original Decaff I still get all the great flavour but none of the caffeine overload. Result!!
Results.Title: All the flavour, none of the caffeine overload

Results.ReviewText: I've tried many times to find a decent Decaf coffee, but always revert to Nescafe Decaf, it by far the tastiest and smoothest Decaf I have tasted. I have given up looking for other blends as I feel Nescafe is the best
Results.Title: Cannot find a better Decaf coffee

Results.ReviewText: Due to the medication I'm on, its important I have a decaf coffee but there aren't many out there that taste normal. Nescafe decaf tastes... Normal.. Now I can have a decent proper coffee without that 'decaf' taste!
Results.Title: A better decaf altogether

Results.ReviewText: Nice strong flavour without the caffeine - ideal for also drinking at night as it doesnt keep you waken - however can be expensive unless on offer which this is very periodically - usually original Nescafe on offer
Results.Title: Caffeine Free

Results.ReviewText: I've been enjoying Nescafé decaf for some time now (after being told to reduce my blood pressure). Immediately thinking my coffee drinking days were over, I was both pleased (& relieved) to find this alternative.
Results.Title: Five star!

Results.ReviewText: It tastes as good if not better than regular coffee and now I don't get migraines and restless legs no matter how much I drink. Very glad I don't have to give up my coffee. The dolce gusto pods are also amazing.
Results.Title: Coffee without migraines or restless legs.

Results.ReviewText: I am very much a fresh coffee bean coffee drinker but when I was advised to go Decafinated coffee I was unsure which brand.  Chose Nescafe and I am certainly not disappointed.  Very surprised how good it tastes
Results.Title: Wonderful rich taste

Results.ReviewText: Mrs F likes to move onto DeCaff in the afternoons, and she finds that this Nescafe Original Decaf is full of flavour, smooth, and just the ticket with a slab of something home made for her mid afternoon break.
Results.Title: Great Tasting DeCaff

Results.ReviewText: i have bought this coffee for the last few months after my friend introduced me to it, beautiful taste, i always look forward to my morning coffee, knowing i have something that tastes as good as nescafe decaf
Results.Title: beautiful taste

Results.ReviewText: I have tried so many different brands of decaff coffee and none have come anywhere near the quality and taste of Nescafe Decaff instant coffee. I did the blindfold taste test and could not tell the difference!
Results.Title: Best Decaff Taste

Results.ReviewText: Bought this as it's decaf and I'm pregnant, so had to reduce my daily caffeine intake. Also prefect if you feel like having a coffee later in the day and want to avoid caffeine. Same taste as the original one!
Results.Title: Excellent taste, perfect for when you're pregnant

Results.ReviewText: I only drink coffee and over the years have tried many brands finally deciding Nescafe had the best flavour.I bought Nescafe original when I was younger. Now I need to have decaf otherwise I get palpitations.
Results.Title: Best tasting coffee

ClientResponses.Response: Thanks very much for letting us know! You never know, you could be a winner :) Fingers crossed & good luck!

Results.ReviewText: Fairly bitter, acrid taste. Not great but it will do as a drink at work.  Would not drink at home.  Suspect I won't be winning the iPhone from this review but I'm not going to lie by saying it's good coffee.
Results.Title: Alright for work

Results.ReviewText: I have always enjoyed drinking Nescafé original, so I thought that I would give the decaf a try to cut down on my caffeine intake. Best thing I ever did. Still the same great taste, but without the caffeine.
Results.Title: Simply great!

Results.ReviewText:
With Nescafe you can be sure of a good,satisfying cup of coffee-home and away! 
I despair of ordering coffee and being disappointed at the lack of taste and the expense. Stay coffee confident with Nescafe!
Results.Title: Coffee Confident

Results.ReviewText: Had to give up caffine, and was rescued by the excellent strong, deep taste of Nescaf Decaff, as good as the original Nescafe, An excellent coffee, no occasion needed, all the same quality, just NO caffine.
Results.Title: Gone but not forgotten

Results.ReviewText: Started drinking this when pregnant with my 1 st child never looked back great taste from a decaffeinated coffee and I have tried a few. 1 st choice every time nice smooth flavour and no bitter after taste.
Results.Title: Great taste all the flavour less the caffeine

Results.ReviewText: I have been purchasing Nescafe Decaff for as long as it has been on the market. So lovely to enjoy a rich roasted all round flavour - who needs caffeine when you have a superb decaffeinated produce as this!
Results.Title: Stunning rich roasted taste

Results.ReviewText: The flavor is far superior to other brands of Decaf found on store shelves today. Once I tried Nescafe I knew this was the best flavor instant coffee and had no bitter aftertaste. Tried and true. The best.
Results.Title: Flavor Par Excellent!

Results.ReviewText: I run a hairdressing salon and have a lot of clients that asked for decaffienated, I have tried a few different brands but Nescafé has come out on top it is the preferred favourite for my ladies and gents
Results.Title: Salon favourite

Results.ReviewText: Having drunk normal coffe for years, I now have to drink decaff. I thought this would be an issue for me as I really liked the ordinary Nescafé coffees, but I was really surprised how good your decaff is.
Results.Title: Great taste, can't really tell it's Decaff

Results.ReviewText: Purchased this as I like decaffenated tea and found this was very smooth and not such a strong taste as normal coffee. Thoroughly enjoyed it and would recommend it to anyone who likes a less bitter taste.
Results.Title: Great taste !
